Subject: [PATCH v3] kset: fix memory leak when kset_register() returns error
Date:   Tue, 25 Oct 2022 15:15:49 +0800
Message-ID: <20221025071549.1280528-1-yangyingliang@huawei.com>
X-Mailer: git-send-email 2.25.1
